      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The engine has severe mechanical issues and currently does not start, and the transmission slips badly when it was last running. The body shows heavy wear, including several deep dents and noticeable rust patches on the wheel wells. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and some missing trim pieces. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it will need to be towed from its current location.",
